Having regard to the Commission Decision 95/319/EC of 12 July 1995 setting up a Committee of Senior Labour Inspectors (1), and in particular Article 5 thereof,
Whereas Article 5 (2) of that Decision provides that the members of the Committee shall be nominated by the Commission on a proposal from the Member States;
Whereas Article 5 (1) of that Decision provides that the Committee shall consist of two representatives from each Member State;
